  <brief_title>Can Iron Lessen Anemia Due to Cancer and Chemotherapy: A Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Injectafer®</brief_title>
  <acronym>IRON CLAD</acronym>
  <official_title>IRON CLAD: Can Iron Lessen Anemia Due to Cancer and Chemotherapy: A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blinded, Controlled Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Injectafer® (Ferric Carboxymaltose Injection) in Adults</official_title>
  <sponsors>
